title: Dababy Interview and more
itunes:title: Dababy Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had Dababy stop by where he spoke about his album with NBA Young Boy, being "Canceled", love for Lizzo, Kanye West and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Senator Lindsey Graham for his tweet suggesting that someone should assinate Putin, and after we opened the phone lines for our listeners to humble us during "Slander the Breakfast Club"
